<div class="content">
    @await Html.PartialAsync("_HeaderEnglish")
    <div class="mainpagepc">
       <div class="mainboxpc">
            <div class="textbodysecondtextcorp">
                <h1>Facial Treatments</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="boxmain1indexpc">
                <div class="box1indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/dermapen.jpeg" class="imgdermpc" alt="Dermapen" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Dermapen</h2>
                        <h5>Dermapen is a microneedling aesthetic treatment that uses a device with microneedles to create micro-perforations in the skin. These small injuries activate the skin’s natural regeneration process, stimulating collagen and elastin production. Ideal for improving skin texture, reducing fine lines, acne scars, enlarged pores, spots, and stretch marks. The procedure is minimally invasive and suitable for various skin types. After the session, mild redness may occur; it's essential to avoid direct sun exposure and apply sunscreen. With periodic sessions, the skin becomes firmer, more even, and rejuvenated...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="FacialTreatments" asp-action="Microneedling" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box2indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/Microdermoabr.jpeg" class="imgderm1pc" alt="Microdermabrasion" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Microdermabrasion</h2>
                        <h5>Diamond-tip microdermabrasion: a non-invasive aesthetic treatment that exfoliates the skin’s outermost layer using diamond tips or fine crystals. It removes dead cells, improves texture, and stimulates cell regeneration. Ideal for treating spots, mild scars, fine lines, open pores, and dull skin. The procedure is quick, painless, and requires no recovery time. After the session, skin appears softer, brighter, and more even. Sunscreen use and sun avoidance are recommended. Multiple sessions enhance results and visibly renew the skin...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="FacialTreatments" asp-action="MicrodermoabrasionFacial" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box3indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/Radiocila.jpg" class="imgdermpc" alt="Radiofrequency Facial Treatment" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Radiofrequency Facial Treatment</h2>
                        <h5>Radiofrequency Facial Treatment is a non-invasive aesthetic treatment that uses electromagnetic waves to heat deep skin layers, stimulating collagen and elastin production. Perfect for reducing sagging, improving facial firmness, smoothing wrinkles, and redefining facial contours. The procedure is painless, relaxing, and requires no downtime. From the first session, the skin appears firmer and more radiant. Results intensify over time. Suitable for all skin types and recommended in multiple sessions for a progressive, natural lifting effect...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="FacialTreatments" asp-action="RadioFrequencyFacial" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="textbodysecondtextcorp">
                <h1>Body Treatments</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="boxmain2indexpc">
                <div class="box4indexpc">
                    <h2>Anti-Cellulite Treatments</h2>
                    <div class="box2anticelpc">
                        <div class="box2anticelpc1">
                            <div class="imgbox1pc">
                                <img src="~/images/cavitation.jpeg" class="imgcavminipc1" alt="Cavitation" />
                                <h4>Cavitation</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="imgbox2pc">
                                <img src="~/images/radiofrecorp.jpeg" class="imgcavminipc2" alt="Radiofrequency for the Body" />
                                <h4>Radiofrequency for the Body</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h1 class="pluscavminipc">+</h1>
                        <div class="box2anticelpc2">
                            <div class="imgbox3pc">
                                <img src="~/images/preso.jpg" class="imgcavminipc3" alt="Pressotherapy" />
                                <h4>Pressotherapy</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="imgbox4pc">
                                <img src="~/images/Vauterapia.jpg" class="imgcavminipc4" alt="Vacuum Therapy" />
                                <h4>Vacuum Therapy</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box4anticetxtpc">
                        <h5>Anti-Cellulite: These treatments combine technologies like vacuum therapy, cavitation, radiofrequency for the body, and pressotherapy to improve skin appearance and reduce volume. Vacuum therapy stimulates circulation and mobilizes localized fat through suction; cavitation uses ultrasound to break down fat cells; radiofrequency tightens the skin by stimulating collagen and elastin; and pressotherapy promotes lymphatic drainage to eliminate toxins and retained fluids. These non-invasive, painless procedures are highly effective when used together. With regular sessions, the skin becomes firmer, smoother, and visibly improved in cellulite and contour...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc btnanti"><a asp-controller="BodyTreatments" asp-action="AntiCelluliteTreatment" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="boxmain3indexpc">
                <div class="box5indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/radiofrecorp.jpeg" class="imgdermpc" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Body Radiofrequency</h2>
                        <h5>Body radiofrequency is a non-invasive aesthetic treatment that uses electromagnetic waves to heat the deep layers of the skin, stimulating collagen production, improving elasticity, and aiding in the elimination of localized fat. Ideal for treating sagging, firming areas such as the abdomen, arms, buttocks, and thighs, and reducing cellulite. The procedure is safe, comfortable, and requires no recovery time. Visible skin tightening and toning from the first sessions, with progressively better results over time...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="BodyTreatments" asp-action="RadiofrequencyBody" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box6indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/cavitation.jpeg" class="imgdermpc" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Cavitation</h2>
                        <h5>Cavitation is a non-invasive aesthetic treatment that uses low-frequency ultrasound to break down fat cells from the inside, facilitating their natural elimination through the lymphatic system. Especially effective for reducing localized fat in the abdomen, thighs, flanks, and buttocks. The procedure is painless, safe, and requires no downtime. With regular sessions, there's a noticeable volume reduction, improved body contour, and smoother skin. Best combined with a balanced diet, hydration, and physical activity for enhanced results...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="BodyTreatments" asp-action="CavitationTreatment" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box7indexpc">
                    <img src="~/images/preso.jpg" class="imgdermpc" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    <div class="dermspainpc">
                        <h2>Pressotherapy</h2>
                        <h5>Pressotherapy is a non-invasive aesthetic treatment that uses controlled air pressure through a pneumatic suit to perform a deep lymphatic massage. It helps eliminate toxins, reduce fluid retention, improve circulation, and relieve the feeling of heavy legs. Ideal as a complement in slimming and anti-cellulite treatments, it also aids in recovery after other procedures. The session is relaxing, safe, and requires no downtime. With continuous sessions, there's noticeable improvement in skin texture, volume reduction, and a general sense of lightness and well-being...</h5>
                        <button class="btn-theme-homepc"><a asp-controller="BodyTreatments" asp-action="Pressotherapy" class="btn-home-page">Want to know more?</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
